data.description: Escape to the countryside with this popular open floor plan! Enjoy your morning coffee overlooking the beautiful POND from your screened-in porch or fish from your own backyard! Soaring cathedral ceilings upon entering the home and throughout. Two bedrooms and a full bath immediately to the left tucked away from the primary suite for privacy. The grand foyer flows into the kitchen with 42'' cabinets and lots of them! Corian counters, pantry and an island/breakfast bar complete this generously sized kitchen. The great room has lots of space for entertaining and boasts hardwood floors and ceiling fan. Primary suite overlooks the pond with a walk-in closet and ensuite. Upstairs you'll find the 4th bedroom with its own loft living area and closet.  Lots of storage in this home! Landscaped withroses and azaleas as well. This home is a diamond in the rough and with a little TLC could be your perfect oasis! The neighborhood has a community pool, park, and fishing ponds. DD2 schools!! Super convenient to Summerville, I-26, Volvo, Boeing, and the beaches. Don't miss this below market deal!
